      "instruction": "<p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 12-15 min or until the basa is cooked through and the vegetables are tender – this is your <strong>Mexican-style basa tray bake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
